         I think this is a great idea when working for faction. It will help get you there faster if not more efficiently IMO. However, in certain situations I can see the uses for this. If your hunting 3 mobs and you have this on your pet, it will do the most good as it will and should stack with all your dots therfore saving you some mana and keeping aggro on your pet. If your pet dies, then there might be some problems. Also if this/these weapons are not LORE, then you could do some outstanding damage and really kick some ass. I think this is not an original idea, but you have my vote of appoval. If you try it, let us know how you did. I am willing to see the effects as well as the DPS and other various things that would go along with this.</P><P>Velous</P><P>"I make dead people."<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
