         DC pet will use any 1h weapon you give it.  I have given my DC pet sword of skyfire to use in grey and it procs alot, atleast once or twice a fight.  I have also given my pet bard only weapons like harmonic sybra or ranger only weapons like lupin dagger and rouge only weapons.  They all proc just fine.  The only problems is once the mob is charmed the procs on them gos to very little.  The only weapons that procs alot that i have found is Sword of sky fire.  I some times put that in pets main hand and use swift blade of luclin in pets off hand to give it the 40% haste it works great if you have alot of money to blow incase you loose the weapons.</P><P>Kylina <BR>60 necro of Xegony</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
